    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The death of a ghost",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.09,
      "endTime": 9.45
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why did the two brothers keep the secret?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.46,
      "endTime": 13.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "For years, villagers believed that Endley farm was haunted.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 13.75,
      "endTime": 18.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The farm was owned by two brothers, Joe and Bob Cox.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 18.87,
      "endTime": 23.73
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They employed a few farmhands, but no one was willing to work there long.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.74,
      "endTime": 29.25
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Every time a worker gave up his job, he told the same story.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.26,
      "endTime": 34.94,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Farm labourers said that they always woke up to find that work had been done overnight.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34.95,
      "endTime": 41.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Hay had been cut and cowsheds had been cleaned.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.59,
      "endTime": 46.02
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A farm worker, who stayed up all night, claimed to have seen a figure cutting corn in the moonlight.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.03,
      "endTime": 53.63
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In time, it became an accepted fact that the Cox brothers employed a conscientious ghost that did most of their work for them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.64,
      "endTime": 64.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "No one suspected that there might be someone else on the farm who had never been seen.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.02,
      "endTime": 70.06,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This was indeed the case.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.07,
      "endTime": 72.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A short time ago, villagers were astonished to learn that the ghost of Endley had died.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.81,
      "endTime": 79.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Short",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "矮的"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Everyone went to the funeral, for the 'ghost' was none other than Eric Cox,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80,
      "endTime": 86.84
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "a third brother who was supposed to have died as a young man.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 86.85,
      "endTime": 91.42,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Young",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "年轻的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "After the funeral, Joe and Bob revealed a secret which they had kept for over fifty years.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 91.43,
      "endTime": 99.47
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Eric had been the eldest son of the family, very much older than his two brothers.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 99.48,
      "endTime": 105.48,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Son",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "儿子"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          },
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He had been obliged to join the army during the Second World War.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.49,
      "endTime": 110.24
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "As he hated army life, he decided to desert his regiment.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 110.25,
      "endTime": 116.12,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When he learnt that he would be sent abroad,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116.13,
      "endTime": 118.98,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "he returned to the farm and his father hid him until the end of the war.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 118.99,
      "endTime": 124.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Fearing the authorities, Eric remained in hiding after the war as well.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 124.41,
      "endTime": 130.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "His father told everybody that Eric had been killed in action.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 130.36,
      "endTime": 135.02,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The only other people who knew the secret were Joe and Bob.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 135.03,
      "endTime": 139.48
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They did not even tell their wives.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.49,
      "endTime": 142.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When their father died they thought it their duty to keep Eric in hiding.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 142.69,
      "endTime": 147.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "All these years, Eric had lived as a recluse.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 147.7,
      "endTime": 152.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He used to sleep during the day and work at night,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 152.66,
      "endTime": 155.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "quite unaware of the fact that he had become the ghost of Endley.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 155.66,
      "endTime": 160.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When he died, however, his brothers found it impossible to keep the secret any longer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 160.6,
      "endTime": 165.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
